<p>A <code>SegmentGroupItem</code> is one option inside a
  <a href="/components/segment-group/"><code>SegmentGroup</code></a>.
  Each item is a <code>&lt;button role="radio"&gt;</code> with
  <code>aria-checked</code> and roving <code>tabindex</code>
  (<code>0</code> when selected, <code>-1</code> otherwise). See
  the <a href="/components/segment-group/">SegmentGroup demo</a>
  for composed examples.</p>
